com.ibm.team.scm.client.events

Interface ICurrentChangeSetEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEvent, IWorkspaceEvent

    public interface ICurrentChangeSetEvent
extends IWorkspaceEvent
    Event type which describes when the current active change set for a workspace connection's component changes.

    0.5
